OL,3,CFirefighters tackle a blaze in a
OL,4,Cderelict building in Bearwood
OL,6,FAround 60 firefighters were called to
OL,7,Ftackle a big blaze in a derelict
OL,8,Fbuilding in Sandwell overnight.
OL,10,FThe fire took place in a three-storey
OL,11,Fcommercial property in Anderson Road
OL,12,Fin Bearwood shortly before 1am on
OL,13,FSunday (May 18). It is an end of
OL,14,Fterrace buiding by the junction with
OL,15,Fthe main high street Bearwood.
OL,17,FInitially four fire crews were called
OL,18,Fto the incident at 1.18am on Sunday
OL,19,F(May 18) 'responding to a fire in a
OL,20,Fderelict building'. No people were
OL,21,Freported to be in the building.
