OL,3,CFirefighters tackle a blaze in a
OL,4,Cderelict building in Bearwood
OL,6,FThe incident was scaled up to 12 crews
OL,7,Fwith a hydraulic platform also called
OL,8,Finto action around 3am.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Fire Service posted: "We
OL,11,Fhave 12 crews in attendance at a fire
OL,12,Fon Anderson Road, Bearwood, Smethwick.
OL,14,F"As a precaution, if you live or work
OL,15,Fnearby, please keep doors and windows
OL,16,Fclosed. Avoid the area, where
OL,17,Fpossible."
