OL,3,CFirefighters tackle a blaze in a
OL,4,Cderelict building in Bearwood
OL,6,FAnderson Road and the main Bearwood
OL,7,FRoad have been closed off to traffic
OL,8,Fwhile firefighters deal with the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FThey are likely to remain closed 'for
OL,12,Fmost of the day', although the police
OL,13,Fwill move the cordon when they are
OL,14,Fable to do so.
OL,16,FAt around 4am the fire service said:
OL,17,F"Good progress is being made bringing
OL,18,Fthe fire under control and protecting
OL,19,Fsurrounding properties. Road closures
OL,20,Fremain in place."
