OL,3,CFirefighters tackle a blaze in a
OL,4,Cderelict building in Bearwood
OL,6,FThe incident was then scaled back to
OL,7,Fsix crews shortly before 5am. And
OL,8,Faround 8am was being further reduced
OL,9,Fto four crews.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Fire Service said:
OL,12,F"Incident will shortly be scaled back
OL,13,Fto 4 crews, damping down hot spots.
OL,15,F"Drone will be brought into use to
OL,16,Fassist due to the structural and
OL,17,Fcomplex nature of the building.
OL,19,F"Bearwood and Anderson Road will
OL,20,Fremain closed for most of the morning,
OL,21,Fwith West Midlands Police support."
