OL,3,CFirefighters tackle a blaze in a
OL,4,Cderelict building in Bearwood
OL,6,FShortly before 9am the fire service
OL,7,Fsaid: "Crews continue to make good
OL,8,Fprogress as our investigation into the
OL,9,Fcause of the fire at a commercial
OL,10,Fpremises is underway.
OL,12,F"Police are managing road closures for
OL,13,Fparts of Bearwood Road and Anderson
OL,14,FRoad which are likely to be in place
OL,15,Ffor most of today (18 May)."
OL,17,FThe cause of the incident is currently
OL,18,Fbeing investigated.
